                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190707-62-off328 t18190707-62-cd329"></join>, 70 yards of moreen, value 2 l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190707-62-victim610" type="victimName">
                     John 
